      "content": "\"let yourself stop and be still\"... that sounds almost like peace. but i can't just sit here and wait for it to get better because i know it won't. the only way the weight actually goes away is if i'm not even here to feel it anymore. does that even make sense? that it just feels like the only real way to get some rest?",
